                <div class=" aboutGameSection">
                    <h1>Does it worth your time?</h1>
                    <p class="indent">
                        Titanfall 2 has been reviewed by everyone with a 9/10 score and it has been called the greatest
                        first person shooter by many. The game is actually a very good first person shooter. It has
                        everything, jumping, double jumping, sliding, wall sliding and huge robots. The campaign story
                        is easy to follow, there is variety in the gameplay and in general it is a very enjoyable
                        experience.
                    </p>
                    <p class="indent">
                        The achievements are easy to do and the chapter select option adds to that. But there is one
                        achievement that will take a lot of time and patience. It is an ingame challenge, time sensitive
                        and skill dependent.
                    </p>
                    <h2>First Playthrough</h2>
                    <p class="indent">
                        For the first playthrough play the campaign in Master difficulty. The game is not that hard and
                        it does not worth in my opinion an extra playthrough just for the difficulty achievements.
                        There is only one collectible and do not worry much about it, because you will miss a few
                        anyway.
                    </p>
