                                    <%= achievements[27].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[29].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[29].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[29].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Collecting all the titan cores will earn you
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[43].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[43].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[43].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Other easy combat achievements you can do as a pilot are
                        <span class=" achievement">
