                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[34].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[34].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="indent">
                        There are only three achievements for the multiplayer:
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[48].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[48].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[48].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[49].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[49].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[49].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[47].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[47].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[47].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, which can be done solo, by creating a private match and using bots.
                    </p>
                    <p class="indent">
                        Now what is left are
                        <span class=" achievement">
                            <%= achievements[0].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[0].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
